' Bonus — Salt UI mockups. Salt is PlantUML's built-in mock-up
' language. Useful when describing UX flows to contributors without
' a screenshot in git LFS. Salt needs @startsalt/@endsalt — embedding
' it inside @startuml + `salt { … }` no longer works as of
' PlantUML 1.2026.x. Each mockup is a separate top-level block so
' the renderer emits one image per panel.

